Worktree
========

Worktree bundles the official Git logo as its menu-bar icon
(`Sources/Worktree/Resources/MenuBarIcon.png`).

  Git Logo by Jason Long
  Licensed under the Creative Commons Attribution 3.0 Unported License
  https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/3.0/
  Source: https://git-scm.com/downloads/logos

No modifications to the logo's design were made; the source SVG was
rasterized to a 1024×1024 PNG for use as an NSStatusItem template image.
